      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text line-height="1.4">
          The September release is jam-packed with great blogs and media mentions to focuse on how Locus is committed to making life easy for customers while building their trust in last mile execution plans. Check out our blog, news and events page and get ready to learn about what’s new in Locus blogs, Locus in the news, upcoming events & webinars and much, much more!
        </mj-text>
