        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="50%">
        <mj-image src="./image-placeholder.png"></mj-image>
        <mj-text line-height="1.25">
          <h3>Owned Vs Outsourced Fleet: What’s Best for Your Fast Retail Business</h3>
          <p>For decades, Walmart has been the undisputed front-runner in US retail sales. One of the major factors that contributed to its success is its tight control over its retail logistics.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="outlined" align="left" href="#">Read the blog</mj-button>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="50%">
        <mj-image src="./image-placeholder.png"></mj-image>
        <mj-text line-height="1.25">
          <h3>Learnings@Locus: What Makes Every Delivery More Efficient than the Last</h3>
          <p>School may make up only a few years of our life but education is a lifetime’s work. And if we pay enough attention to the world, learning becomes a constant companion.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="outlined" align="left" href="#">Read the blog</mj-button>
