    <mj-section background-color="#F0E0FF">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text font-size="20px" font-weight="bold" line-height="1.45" align="center">
          New Whitepaper
          <h5 style="margin:1em 0 0 0;">Buying vs. Building Logistics Software: How to Choose?</h5>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text line-height="1.3">
          <p>Last mile operations around the country are being tested due to soaring demand & rising consumer expectations. It has become more critical than ever to deploy advanced logistics solutions to drive higher operational efficiencies and improve customer experience. This white paper is a deep dive into keeping key decision-making levers in mind when choosing between buying or building logistics software to get the best out of your last mile.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="outlined" border="1.5px solid #F0E0FF" href="#">Get the whitepaper</mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text font-size="20px" font-weight="bold" align="center" padding-bottom="25px">
