        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="50%">
        <mj-image src="./image-placeholder.png"></mj-image>
        <mj-text line-height="1.4">
          <h3>This Startup Is Solving Last-Mile Delivery Problem with Tech | Delivers 650 Million Orders!</h3>
          <p>Recently, we interacted with Mr. Nishith Rastogi, Founder and CEO, Locus, and asked him about the mission and vision of his startup, and how they are empower supply chain with tech and ideas.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="outlined" align="left" href="#">Find out how</mj-button>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="50%">
        <mj-image src="./image-placeholder.png"></mj-image>
        <mj-text line-height="1.4">
          <h3>The significance of seamless dispatch management for e&#8209;commerce players</h3>
          <p>Dispatch management is a multi-step process that includes order capture and allocation, slot booking, parcel sorting, capacity management, route planning, carrier selection, and the tracking of parcels up to their delivery.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="outlined" align="left" href="#">Check it out</mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#FFE0D4">
